been sort of rejected since\nthe early modern movement, sort
of discussions of aesthetics\nand what constitutes beauty,
but beauty is generally what\neverybody wants in their life,
as well as civicness, and\ngenerosity, and authenticity.
And so this kind of declaration\nof a value system I felt
